<li>Richard Swedberg, <i>Max Weber and the Idea of Economic Sociology</i>. Princeton: Princeton University Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/069107013X" class="internal">ISBN 0-691-07013-X</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Marianne_Weber" title="Marianne Weber">Weber, Marianne</a> (1926/1988). <i>Max Weber: A Biography</i>. New Brunswick: Transaction Books. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0471923338" class="internal">ISBN 0-471-92333-8</a></li>
<li>Problems in European Civilization, Protestantism and Capitalism: The Weber Thesis and Its Critics, ed: Robert Green, D.C. Heath and Company, 1959.</li>
</ul>
