<li><a href="http://media.pfeiffer.edu/lridener/DSS/Weber/WEBRPER.HTML" class="external text" title="http://media.pfeiffer.edu/lridener/DSS/Weber/WEBRPER.HTML" rel="nofollow">Max Weber – The person</a></li>
<li><a href="http://media.pfeiffer.edu/lridener/DSS/Weber/WEBERW3.HTML" class="external text" title="http://media.pfeiffer.edu/lridener/DSS/Weber/WEBERW3.HTML" rel="nofollow">More of Weber on Ideal Types</a></li>
